r=\"\"><svg role=\"progressbar\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" aria-valuenow=\"0\" aria-valuemin=\"0\" aria-valuemax=\"1\" class=\"shrink-0\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"11\" fill=\"none\" stroke-width=\"2\" class=\"stroke-current/25\"></circle><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"11\" fill=\"none\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-dasharray=\"69.11503837897544\" stroke-dashoffset=\"69.11503837897544\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" transform=\"rotate(-90 12 12)\" class=\"transition-all\"></circle></svg><span class=\"grid flex-1 *:my-auto *:row-start-1 *:col-start-1\"><span class=\"truncate transition-[opacity,translate,color]\">Commission</span><span class=\"truncate transition-[opacity,translate] opacity-0 translate-y-full pointer-events-none\"></span></span><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-down shrink-0 transition-transform mx-0.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m6 9 6 6 6-6\"></path></svg></button><div data-state=\"closed\" id=\"radix-_R_1av5u9flb_\" hidden=\"\" data-toc-popover-content=\"\" class=\"overflow-hidden\"></div></header></div><article id=\"nd-page\" data-full=\"false\" class=\"flex flex-col w-full max-w-[900px] mx-auto [grid-area:main] px-4 py-6 gap-4 md:px-6 md:pt-8 xl:px-8 xl:pt-14 xl:layout:[--fd-toc-width:268px]\"><h1 class=\"text-[1.75em] font-semibold\">Commission</h1><p class=\"text-lg text-fd-muted-foreground mb-0\">Set up commission rules for your staff and generate detailed salary slips</p><div class=\"flex flex-row gap-2 items-center border-b pb-6\"><button class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md p-2 font-medium transition-colors duration-100 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-fd-ring border bg-fd-secondary text-fd-secondary-foreground hover:bg-fd-accent hover:text-fd-accent-foreground px-2 py-1.5 text-xs gap-2 [&amp;_svg]:size-3.5 [&amp;_svg]:text-fd-muted-foreground\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-copy\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><rect width=\"14\" height=\"14\" x=\"8\" y=\"8\" rx=\"2\" ry=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M4 16c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V4c0-1.1.9-2 2-2h10c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2\"></path></svg>Copy Markdown</button><button type=\"button\" aria-haspopup=\"dialog\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"radix-_R_9qav5u9flb_\" data-state=\"closed\" class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md p-2 font-medium transition-colors duration-100 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-fd-ring border bg-fd-secondary text-fd-secondary-foreground hover:bg-fd-accent hover:text-fd-accent-foreground px-2 py-1.5 text-xs gap-2 data-[state=open]:bg-fd-accent data-[state=open]:text-fd-accent-foreground\">Open<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-down size-3.5 text-fd-muted-foreground\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m6 9 6 6 6-6\"></path></svg></button></div><div class=\"prose flex-1\"><p>The Commission page is where you define how much each staff member earns from the services they perform, and view a live breakdown of what they&#x27;ve earned. NxCut calculates everything automatically based on real sales data.</p>\n<p>Click <strong>Commission</strong> in the left menu to get started.</p>\n<div class=\"flex gap-2 my-4 rounded-xl border bg-fd-card p-3 ps-1 text-sm text-fd-card-foreground shadow-md\" style=\"--callout-color:var(--color-fd-info, var(--color-fd-muted))\"><div role=\"none\" class=\"w-0.5 bg-(--callout-color)/50 rounded-sm\"></div><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-info size-5 -me-0.5 fill-(--callout-color) text-fd-card\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"M12 16v-4\"></path><path d=\"M12 8h.01\"></path></svg><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-2 min-w-0 flex-1\"><div class=\"text-fd-muted-foreground prose-no-margin empty:hidden\"><p>Commission is only accessible to admin users.</p></div></div></div>\n<p>The page is split into two sections: <strong>Team Member Commissions</strong> (your commission rules) and <strong>Commission Calculations</strong> (the live earnings breakdown).</p>\n<hr/>\n<h2 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"team-member-commissions\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#team-member-commissions\" class=\"peer\">Team Member Commissions</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h2>\n<p>This section lists all the commission rules you&#x27;ve set up. If no rules have been created yet, it will show &quot;No commission settings found — add a commission setting to get started.&quot;</p>\n<hr/>\n<h2 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"setting-up-a-commission-rule\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#setting-up-a-commission-rule\" class=\"peer\">Setting up a commission rule</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h2>\n<p>Click <strong>+ Add Commission</strong> in the top right. A form will pop up.</p>\n<div class=\"fd-steps\"><div class=\"fd-step\"><p>Select a <strong>Team Member</strong> from the dropdown.</p></div><div class=\"fd-step\"><p>The <strong>Services Commission</strong> section is enabled by default. This means the staff member earns commission on the services they perform.</p></div><div class=\"fd-step\"><p>Choose the <strong>Default commission type</strong>:</p><ul>\n<li><strong>Fixed rate</strong> — a set percentage applied to every sale they make</li>\n</ul></div><div class=\"fd-step\"><p>Enter the <strong>Default rate</strong> — the percentage they&#x27;ll earn (e.g., 30%).</p></div><div class=\"fd-step\"><p>Set the <strong>Sales period</strong> — how often commission is calculated. The default is <strong>Monthly</strong>. NxCut will show you exactly when the first and following periods will be.</p></div><div class=\"fd-step\"><p>Use the <strong>Sample calculation</strong> box to double-check your setup. Enter a sale amount and NxCut will show you the exact commission calculation — including the threshold, commissionable amount, and final payout.</p></div><div class=\"fd-step\"><p>Click <strong>Create Commission</strong> to save.</p></div></div>\n<div class=\"flex gap-2 my-4 rounded-xl border bg-fd-card p-3 ps-1 text-sm text-fd-card-foreground shadow-md\" style=\"--callout-color:var(--color-fd-info, var(--color-fd-muted))\"><div role=\"none\" class=\"w-0.5 bg-(--callout-color)/50 rounded-sm\"></div><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-info size-5 -me-0.5 fill-(--callout-color) text-fd-card\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"M12 16v-4\"></path><path d=\"M12 8h.01\"></path></svg><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-2 min-w-0 flex-1\"><div class=\"text-fd-muted-foreground prose-no-margin empty:hidden\"><p>The sample calculation updates in real time as you type — use it to make sure the numbers look right before saving.</p></div></div></div>\n<hr/>\n<h2 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"commission-calculations\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#commission-calculations\" class=\"peer\">Commission Calculations</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h2>\n<p>Below the commission rules is the <strong>Commission Calculations</strong> table — a live breakdown of what each staff member has earned for the current period.</p>\n<p>At the top you&#x27;ll see four summary cards:</p>\n<div class=\"relative overflow-auto prose-no-margin my-6\"><table><thead><tr><th>Card</th><th>What it shows</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Team Members</td><td>Number of staff with sales in this period</td></tr><tr><td>Total Sales</td><td>Combined revenue across all staff</td></tr><tr><td>Total Commission</td><td>Total commission owed to the team</td></tr><tr><td>Avg Commission %</td><td>Average commission rate across the team</td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n<p>The table below shows each staff member with:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Sales Count</strong> — number of sales completed</li>\n<li><strong>Total Sales</strong> — their total revenue</li>\n<li><strong>Commission Type</strong> — their commission setup, or a <strong>No Setup</strong> badge if none has been configured</li>\n<li><strong>Commission Rate</strong> — their percentage</li>\n<li><strong>Commission Amount</strong> — what they&#x27;ve earned</li>\n<li><strong>Actions</strong> — an eye icon to view the breakdown, and a salary slip icon to open their slip</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Click <strong>Export CSV</strong> to download the full table for payroll processing.</p>\n<hr/>\n<h2 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"salary-slip\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#salary-slip\" class=\"peer\">Salary Slip</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h2>\n<p>Click the salary slip icon next to any team member to open their <strong>Salary Slip</strong>. This is a full payroll breakdown that can be filled in and downloaded.</p>\n<p>The slip is headed with your salon&#x27;s name and labelled as <strong>Payroll Advice</strong>. It shows the staff member&#x27;s name, their occupancy percentage, free hours, the month, and their title.</p>\n<p><strong>Earnings section</strong></p>\n<p>A table where you can enter values for each earning type:</p>\n<div class=\"relative overflow-auto prose-no-margin my-6\"><table><thead><tr><th>Earning</th><th>Description</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Basic Salary</td><td>Their fixed monthly salary</td></tr><tr><td>Over Time</td><td>Overtime hours worked</td></tr><tr><td>Voucher</td><td>Commission from voucher sales</td></tr><tr><td>Allowance</td><td>Any allowances paid</td></tr><tr><td>Products</td><td>Commission from product sales</td></tr><tr><td>Bonus</td><td>Any bonus payment</td></tr><tr><td>EOS</td><td>End of service accrual</td></tr><tr><td>Target</td><td>Target-based incentives</td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n<p>Each row has editable fields for rate, days, and hours. The <strong>Total Earning</strong> is calculated automatically.</p>\n<p><strong>Deductions section</strong></p>\n<p>Enter any amounts to deduct:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Deduction</li>\n<li>Cash advance</li>\n<li>Additional deduction</li>\n</ul>\n<p>The <strong>Total Deduction</strong> and final <strong>Net Salary</strong> are calculated automatically at the bottom.</p>\n<p>Once the slip is complete, click <strong>Download XLS</strong> to save it as a spreadsheet, or <strong>Close</strong> to exit without saving.</p>\n<hr/>\n<h2 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"quick-reference\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#quick-reference\" class=\"peer\">Quick reference</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h2>\n<div class=\"relative overflow-auto prose-no-margin my-6\"><table><thead><tr><th>Feature</th><th>Details</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Commission rules</td><td>Set per staff member with a fixed rate and sales period</td></tr><tr><td>Sample calculator</td><td>Preview the commission payout before saving</td></tr><tr><td>No Setup badge</td><td>Staff member has sales but no commission rule configured</td></tr><tr><td>Calculations table</td><td>Live monthly breakdown per staff member</td></tr><tr><td>Export CSV</td><td>Download the full calculations for payroll</td></tr><tr><td>Salary slip</td><td>Full payroll advice with earnings, deductions, and net salary — downloadable as XLS</td></tr><tr><td>Access</td><td>Admin only</td></tr></tbody></table></div></div><div class=\"@container grid gap-4 grid-cols-2\"><a class=\"flex flex-col gap-2 rounded-lg border p-4 text-sm transition-colors hover:bg-fd-accent/80 hover:text-fd-accent-foreground @max-lg:col-span-full\" href=\"/docs/team\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 font-medium\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-left -mx-1 size-4 shrink-0 rtl:rotate-180\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m15 18-6-6 6-6\"></path></svg><p>Team Management</p></div><p class=\"text-fd-muted-foreground truncate\">Add staff, set their schedules, and control what they can access</p></a><a class=\"flex flex-col gap-2 rounded-lg border p-4 text-sm transition-colors hover:bg-fd-accent/80 hover:text-fd-accent-foreground @max-lg:col-span-full text-end\" href=\"/docs/reporting\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 font-medium flex-row-reverse\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-right -mx-1 size-4 shrink-0 rtl:rotate-180\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m9 18 6-6-6-6\"></path></svg><p>Reporting &amp; Analytics</p></div><p class=\"text-fd-muted-foreground tr